title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week 3
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for Week 3. Big Cat is a fresh off a heart breaking Game of the Year Loss and almost never talked to an employee again for texting him to rub it in on Saturday night. Also Dave continues the new segment of reading this week's Top 20 Bloggers.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
